casebody.data:
Miguelis DIAZ, etc., Respondent,
v.
WYCKOFF HEIGHTS MEDICAL CENTER et al., Defendants, 297 Schaeffer Street Realty Corp. et al., Appellants. 2018-132 Court of Appeals of New York. April 3, 2018

Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that the order sought to be appealed from does not finally determine the action within the meaning of the Constitution.
